    "logicErrorDescription": "The PR changes the TAKEOFF waypoint acceptance logic for fixed-wing to be altitude-based (like multirotor) rather than requiring horizontal proximity. This addresses incorrect mission progression around hand-launch / climbout situations where the navigator could accept or delay the takeoff waypoint inappropriately, producing unexpected behavior; the discussion shows this was an intended behavioral fix though there is some design debate, so confidence is medium."
