    "logicErrorDescription": "Yes â€” the PR fixes a logic bug where mission feasibility was evaluated too early (before the geofence and global position were available), producing incorrect startup behavior such as arming then immediate shutdown. The change defers feasibility checks until prerequisites are loaded and adds rechecks on activation, and reviewers/tests confirm it corrects the erroneous outcomes."
