    "logicErrorDescription": "Yes â€” the PR fixes a logic error: failure to initialize MissionBase::_mission when dataman read/write times out could leave the navigator in an invalid state and busy-loop in updateDatamanCache(). The change constrains the loading loop and ensures mission data is reset even on write/read failures, preventing the infinite-loop/incorrect-state behavior."
