    "isLogicError": true,
    "logicErrorDescription": "The PR changes control flow so the terrain avoidance check is not executed for the idle mission navigation item. The previous behavior ran the check even after a mission ended (idle state), which is an incorrect conditional/state-handling issue causing unintended behavior; the change fixes this logic error by skipping the check in the idle case."
