    },
    "isLogicError": true,
    "logicErrorDescription": "Yes â€” this PR fixes a logic error where gimbal orientation replayed too late, causing photos to be taken while the gimbal was still pitching. The change replays cached gimbal commands earlier (before reaching the waypoint) and adds a check to avoid orienting while on the ground/climbing, correcting the timing/state transition that produced the incorrect behavior."
