    "isLogicError": true,
    "logicErrorDescription": "Yes â€” the PR fixes a logic error where RTL handlers did not initialize their mission member, leaving the handler in an incorrect state (index -1) and causing 'No valid mission' / dataman read errors. The change explicitly loads and passes the existing mission into the handlers at construction, ensuring correct state initialization; SITL tests and logs provided show the issue is resolved."
