          "created_at": "2025-07-10T18:53:34Z",
          "body": "",
          "state": "APPROVED",
          "type": "review"
        },
        {
          "author": "sfuhrer",
          "created_at": "2025-07-11T07:10:36Z",
          "body": "Thanks!",
          "state": "APPROVED",
          "type": "review"
        }
      ]
    },
    "isLogicError": true,
    "logicErrorDescription": "Yes â€” the PR addresses a logic error where isLanding() remained true outside the actual landing segment for multi-land missions, causing the vehicle to continue the mission instead of executing RTL. The change restricts isLanding() to the range between land_start_index and land_index, correcting the incorrect state/conditional logic; SITL testing confirms the behavior fix."
